  <scopecontent id="aspace_3a717a9e47c03ba83f97fb41f82a89b9">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes scrapbooks, photographs, correspondence, rush books, bylaws, annual reports, newsletters, newspaper clippings, pamphlets, and ephemera of fraternities and sororities at Cornell University. Also, t-shirt from Cornell Greek Week, 2003.</p><p> Annual reports from the Fraternity and Sorority Advisory Council, 1997-2009; Guide and Map of the Fraternities &amp; Sororities, 2003-2009; and brochures.</p>  </scopecontent>
